title: Snaps - Who could replace Jimbo Fisher at Texas A&M? Clemson QB controversy? Bo Nix in Heisman race?
itunes:title: Snaps - Who could replace Jimbo Fisher at Texas A&M? Clemson QB controversy? Bo Nix in Heisman race?
description:
Aaron Murray and T-Bob Hebert discuss which coaching candidates could be in line to replace Jimbo Fisher if Texas A&M continues to slide. They later debate if Dabo Swinney and Clemson have a quarterback controversy between DJ Uiagalelei and freshman Cade Klubnik as well as whether Oregon quarterback Bo Nix has put his name in the Heisman race. #Volume #Herd #ColinCowherd
